DROP TABLE Book_Copy;

SET LINESIZE 200;
SET PAGESIZE 200;
SET DEFINE OFF;


COLUMN copyID         FORMAT A8;
COLUMN bookStatus     FORMAT A15;
COLUMN bookCondition  FORMAT A15;
COLUMN bookID         FORMAT A8;

CREATE TABLE Book_Copy (
    copyID         VARCHAR2(6) NOT NULL,
    bookStatus     VARCHAR2(20) NOT NULL,
    bookCondition  VARCHAR2(50) NOT NULL,
    bookID         VARCHAR2(6) NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (copyID),
    FOREIGN KEY (bookID) REFERENCES book(bookID),
    CONSTRAINT chk_copyID_format CHECK (REGEXP_LIKE(copyID, '^C[0-9]{5}$')),
    CONSTRAINT chk_bookID_fk_format CHECK (REGEXP_LIKE(bookID, '^B[0-9]{5}$'))
);
